    "Risk Factors and Limitations": [
      "Potential challenges in accurately estimating activation statistics in real-time, which may affect the adaptability of the quantization scheme.",
      "The need for careful tuning of hyperparameters related to the dynamic quantization process to ensure optimal performance.",
      "Limitations in generalizing the findings to larger and more complex models may necessitate further investigation."
    ]
  }
}
``` 

This refined proposal is clear, concise, and aligns with existing research while presenting a novel approach to model compression. It sets the groundwork for impactful contributions to the field of information-theoretic machine learning.
