r approach to existing empirical methods for model compression'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['The complexity of deriving information-theoretic bounds for deep learning models may be high', 'The novel compression algorithms may not achieve the theoretical bounds in practice due to implementation limitations', 'The evaluation metrics used may not fully capture the trade-offs between compression and performance']}
